entry.request: PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbpedia-owl: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> SELECT ?abstract ?comment ?image ?wikipedia WHERE { dbpedia:Intercalated_disc rdfs:comment ?comment . dbpedia:Intercalated_disc dbpedia-owl:abstract ?abstract . dbpedia:Intercalated_disc foaf:isPrimaryTopicOf ?wikipedia . OPTIONAL { dbpedia:Intercalated_disc foaf:depiction ?image . } FILTER (LANG(?abstract)='en' && LANG(?comment)='en') }
